comments.content:
"E.A.G.L.E.S" (the capital letters) is **[Postino](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317125523/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Adobe&ffam=Postino%20-%20Regular&fid=b4e4da99ef08b5c0ea6dfea3719de74c&fsize=60&text=EAGLES&fit=1)** by Timothy Donaldson [1998]  
"will loar high like eagles" is **[Banshee](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317125523/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Adobe&ffam=Banshee%20-%20Regular&fid=b086706327e21f7d8540b78a5b922e44&fsize=60&text=will%20loar%20high%20like%20eagles&wrap=2)** also by Timothy Donaldson [1997]
